<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>Endpoints tool window</b></p><p>For REST controllers, use the dedicated <span class="control">Endpoints</span> tool window to list all endpoints with their methods and URLs. The tool window also lets you quickly create an HTTP request to the selected endpoint and generate an OpenAPI Specification.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/restapi_endpoints.png" alt="The Endpoints tool window" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>